1. Install WordPress 2.1 on the same server as your Nucleus install.
2. Create all the users you need (or you can let the script create the users for you).
3. Place the nucleus folder in your wp-admin/import folder.
4. Navigate to http://your-wordpress-blog/wp-admin/import/nucleus.
5. Email me at spamtastic@ketsugi.com if you have any problems.
6. Alternatively, file a bug report at the tracker: http://sourceforge.net/tracker/?group_id=171800

